name: Nature-Cyber Hybrid Avatar #67
description: This avatar beautifully merges nature and technology, with cybernetic enhancements and vibrant foliage intricately woven into the design. The glowing, green elements complement the soft features of the character, representing the seamless fusion of life and technology in the RPine DEX aggregator collection.
